[SAGA_RECONCILIATION]
Problem:StateFrag/RaceCond/GoalDrift;
Headers:X-Saga-ID(UUIDv4); X-Parent-Span; X-Agent-Persona;
Lifecycle:1.Init(RegisterSaga/Boundaries) 2.ParallelExec(Sandbox) 3.VerifyHandshake(Schema/DiffScan/ConflictScan) 4.ConflictMatrix 5.Compensate/Commit(TagGit);
